{"tid":1941586,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 係咪想手足係立會選舉好有代表性咁輸？","createTime":"2020-03-24T13:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T13:33:21.000Z","uid":263192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"194ace848a09b98d7089c2589e91769e8cd77941","tid":1941586,"uid":263192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"講清楚呢場選舉嘅一樣野<br />\n就係你張票<strong>唔單止係代表你自己咁簡單</strong><br />\n呢場選戰係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">非建制vs建制</span>嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>大戰<br />\n而你持有果票就係<strong>代表緊非建制、代表黃絲</strong><br />\n到時出黎係會多左黃嘅投喇，但都會多藍嘅投 <br />\n係整體都多<br />\n換言之<strong>呢場選舉好有機會好似區選咁打破之前嘅投票紀錄 </strong><br />\n咁即係點呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即係呢個將會係香港史上暫時最有代表性同最具影響力嘅選舉</span> <br />\n按之前區選嘅64比係遠遠唔夠攻入立會<br />\n呢個係事實<br />\n依家非建制入面嘅諗法已經好分裂 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地呢場選舉輸左<br />\n將會係好有代表性咁輸 </span><br />\n麻煩大家爭爭氣<br />\n起碼圍內初選左先<br />\n<strong>唔好咁快話唔投</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5iKZBO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5iKZBO.jpg&h=d3752650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>致候選人的公開信</strong><br />\n光復議會 我要初選 聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://pe.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpe.hkpetitions.com&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=487b8ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pe.hkpetitions.com</a><br />\n<br />\nChannel <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkpetitions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpetitions&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=b48b8f77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpetitions</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">泛民、本土、獨派、焦土 <br />\n你幾時聽過對面咁多派系？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，團結一次咁多啦</span></span>"},{"pid":